			The first 50 supporters who joined the Cowsay farm early. Each holder is eligible for the
			Genesis NFT airdrop: <strong>Cowsay #001: Genesis</strong>.
		</p>

		<div class="mb-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-yellow-500/50 bg-yellow-500/10 p-6">
			<p class="mb-3 font-semibold text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400">
				⚠️ Important: Claim Your NFT
			</p>
			<p class="mb-4 text-textColor">
				If your wallet is listed below, you are eligible for the Genesis NFT airdrop. You
				<strong> must claim your NFT</strong> through DRIP Studio to receive it.
			</p>
			<p class="text-muted text-sm">
				The airdrop will begin once we collect 50 wallet addresses. Holders also get priority on
				future $COWSAY token claims.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
			<Button href="/token/">
				← Back to Token
			</Button>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Section 2: Holder List -->
	<section class="mb-12">
		<div class="mb-6 rounded-lg border border-green-500 bg-black p-4 font-mono text-sm">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
				<span class="text-green-500">$</span>
				<span class="text-green-500">cat genesis-holders.txt</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-6 rounded-lg border border-accent bg-accent/5 p-6">
			<div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between">
				<h2 class="title text-xl">Genesis Holders ({holders.length})</h2>
				<p class="text-muted text-sm">Total eligible wallets</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="rounded-lg border border-green-500 bg-black p-4">
			<div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm">
				<span class="text-green-500">$</span>
				<span class="text-green-500">./list-holders.sh</span>
			</div>
			<div class="overflow-x-auto">
				<table class="min-w-full text-left text-sm">
					<thead class="text-green-500">
						<tr>
							<th class="pb-2 pr-4 font-semibold">#</th>
							<th class="pb-2 pr-4 font-semibold">Name</th>
							<th class="pb-2 pr-4 font-semibold">Wallet Address</th>
							<th class="pb-2 font-semibold">Explorer</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody class="text-textColor">
						{holders.map((holder, index) => (
							<tr class="border-t border-green-500/20">
								<td class="py-3 pr-4 font-mono text-xs">{String(index + 1).padStart(2, "0")}</td>
								<td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">{holder.name}</td>
								<td class="py-3 pr-4 font-mono text-xs break-all">{holder.wallet}</td>
								<td class="py-3">
									<a
										class="cactus-link text-xs"
										href={`https://solscan.io/account/${holder.wallet}`}
										target="_blank"
										rel="noopener noreferrer"
									>
										View →
									</a>
								</td>
							</tr>
						))}
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Section 3: Claim Instructions -->
	<section class="mb-12">
		<h2 class="title mb-6 text-2xl">How to Claim Your NFT</h2>
		<div class="space-y-4">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-accent bg-accent/5 p-6">
				<h3 class="title mb-4 text-lg">Step-by-Step Instructions</h3>
				<ol class="space-y-3 text-sm">
					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<span class="flex-shrink-0 font-mono text-green-500">1.</span>
						<span>
							<strong>Connect your wallet</strong> that matches the address listed above to DRIP Studio.
						</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<span class="flex-shrink-0 font-mono text-green-500">2.</span>
						<span>
							Navigate to the <strong>Cowsay #001: Genesis</strong> collection on DRIP Studio.
						</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<span class="flex-shrink-0 font-mono text-green-500">3.</span>
						<span>
							Look for your wallet address in the airdrop list and <strong>claim your NFT</strong>.
						</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<span class="flex-shrink-0 font-mono text-green-500">4.</span>
						<span>
							Once claimed, your Genesis NFT will appear in your wallet as a compressed NFT (cNFT).
						</span>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</div>

			<div class="rounded-lg border border-accent p-6">
				<h3 class="title mb-4 text-lg">Benefits for Genesis Holders</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
					<li>• <strong>Priority access</strong> to future $COWSAY token claims</li>
					<li>• Exclusive Genesis NFT (Early Supporter edition)</li>
					<li>• Recognition as one of the first 50 supporters of the Cowsay ecosystem</li>
					<li>• Special perks in future airdrops and community events</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Section -->
	<div class="rounded-lg border-2 border-accent bg-accent/10 p-6 text-center">
		<p class="mb-4 font-semibold">Have questions about claiming your NFT?</p>
		<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
